  "text": "The optimal difference-based estimator in [CITATION_1] remains widely used in practice, and the optimal sequence idea has been used elsewhere. For instance, [CITATION_2] and [CITATION_3] applied the optimal sequence idea to estimate the variance function in nonparametric regression; [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] [CITATION_7] applied it in semiparametric partially linear regression models. [CITATION_8] require a homoscedastic nonparametric regression model and, in practice, it is not uncommon that the errors have different variances or be correlated to each other. This motivates us to propose an optimal difference-based variance estimation in heteroscedastic nonparametric regression.",
